ed="T" n="0743a19"/><persName key="A009682">釋乘恩</persName>，不知何許人也。肇從志學，知遍<lb
ed="T" n="0743a20"/>尋師，凡廁黌堂，必窮義路。常訓門人曰：<lb
ed="T" n="0743a21"/>「好學近乎智，力行近乎仁。仁智稍成，是殊<lb
ed="T" n="0743a22"/>名同實，趨菩薩地，若下坂之走丸耳。」<persName key="A009682">恩</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0743a23"/>樂人為學，不忘講導。及<date notBefore-iso="+0755-02-20" key="j19968681997410" notAfter-iso="+0756-08-15"><name>天寶</name>末</date>，<placeName key="PL000000042002">關中</placeName>版蕩<ptr target="#n382"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0743a24"/>因避地<placeName key="PL000000045043">姑臧</placeName>。旅泊之間，嗟彼密邇<ptr type="glossary" target="#g952"/><ref type="place" target="#PL000000041553">羌虜之<lb
ed="T" n="0743a25"/>封</ref><ptr type="glossary" target="#g953"/>，極尚經、論之學。<persName key="A009682">恩</persName>化其內眾，勉其成功，<lb
ed="T" n="0743a26"/>深染華風，悉登義府。自是重撰《百法論疏》<lb
ed="T" n="0743a27"/>并鈔，行于<ref type="place" target="#PL000000045043">西土</ref>。其疏祖<persName key="A001019">慈恩</persName>而宗<persName key="A001464">潞府</persName>，大<lb
ed="T" n="0743a28"/>抵同而少聞異，終後弟子傳布。迨<date from-iso="+0863-03-27" key="j20363502036379" to-iso="+0863-04-25">咸通四年<lb
ed="T" n="0743a29"/>三月</date>中，<placeName key="PL000000045051">西涼</placeName>僧<persName key="A009689">法信</persName>精研此道，稟本道節度<pb ed="T" n="0743b" xml:id="T50.2061.0743b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0743b01"/>使<persName key="A009685">張義朝</persName>表進<persName key="A009682">恩</persName>之著述，勅令兩街三學<ptr type="glossary" target="#g182"/>大<lb
ed="T" n="0743b02"/>德等詳定，實堪行用。勅依，<ref type="person" target="#A009689">其僧</ref>賜紫衣，充<lb
ed="T" n="0743b03"/><ref type="place" target="#PL000000046807">本道</ref>大德焉。</p>
